§I OPEN-QUESTIONS
  ⟦
    OQ.01 · should spec amendments require new lifecycle (DRAFT→...) or inline edit with trailer-only?
             · default : inline edit + git-trailer · revisit if drift becomes a problem
    OQ.02 · how should specs/grand-vision/ + specs/infinity-engine/ subdirs interact with NN-numbered specs?
             · default : subdirs are sketching-space · graduate to NN when concrete
    OQ.03 · should there be a "SOVEREIGN-AMENDMENT" mechanism where Apocky can override the gates in emergency?
             · default : yes · git --no-verify + post-hoc spec amendment within 7d · ¬ silent override
    OQ.04 · do MNEME-persisted decisions count as specs?
             · default : no · MNEME is operational memory · specs are canonical authoritative
    OQ.05 · how does PRISM_v13.md (in LoA v13 repo) interact with this discipline?
             · default : LoA v13 specs/* are scoped to that repo · adopt same discipline locally · cross-repo coordination is project-level
